data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence boasts a spacious and inviting open floor plan that's perfect for both living and entertaining. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers a host of fantastic features that are sure to delight.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the seamless flow of the open floor plan, which creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The living area is bathed in natural light, creating an inviting space for gatherings.     The primary suite, located on the second story, is designed for comfort and relaxation, featuring an expansive walk-in closet that will easily accommodate your wardrobe and storage needs.    For those who enjoy leisure and entertainment, the second level also includes an additional game room/media space. Whether you're into gaming, movies, or simply need a space to unwind, this versatile area offers endless possibilities.    Step outside into your large fenced backyard and discover a private oasis perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply basking in the sun. The patio is an ideal spot for al fresco dining, barbecues, or sipping your morning coffee while enjoying the fresh air.    Convenience is key with this home's location. You'll be just a stone's throw away from shopping centers and a variety of restaurants, making dining out and retail therapy a breeze. Plus, the neighborhood itself is welcoming and family-friendly, with excellent schools nearby.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home your own. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
